{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-cmake-gtest, ament-lint-auto, ament-lint-common, plansys2-msgs, plansys2-pddl-parser, pluginlib, rclcpp, rclcpp-lifecycle }:
